title: China to boost cultural ties with Sri Lanka: ambassador (The Central People's Government of the ...
text: ( Source : The Central People's Government of the People's Republic of China ) COLOMBO - China attaches great importance to Sri Lanka 's economic and social development needs, Chinese Ambassador to Sri Lanka Yi Xianliang said on Oct 23 .
